  "detailed_description": "A classic for great fun, a virtual and improved chess game!<br />\r\nYour objective is to get the checkmate on the enemy king, but it will not be easy to get close to him with so many pieces involved to protect him.<br />\r\nThe game also shows the possible moves with each piece, thus making it easier to play or even learn!<br />\r\nPut a time limit and win whoever knocks over pieces in less time, or put no time limit and the winner will be who can give the checkmate!<br />\r\nYou can have fun with friends or with the whole family!<br />\r\nLearn how to play or improve your chess skills in a fun way.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nProtect you king from a checkmate!",
  "about_the_game": "A classic for great fun, a virtual and improved chess game!<br />\r\nYour objective is to get the checkmate on the enemy king, but it will not be easy to get close to him with so many pieces involved to protect him.<br />\r\nThe game also shows the possible moves with each piece, thus making it easier to play or even learn!<br />\r\nPut a time limit and win whoever knocks over pieces in less time, or put no time limit and the winner will be who can give the checkmate!<br />\r\nYou can have fun with friends or with the whole family!<br />\r\nLearn how to play or improve your chess skills in a fun way.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nProtect you king from a checkmate!",
